{
  "_schema": "ai-os/runtime-config/profiles",
  "_version": "1.0.0",
  "_sprint": "C",
  "_why": "Per-task-class parameter profiles applied at runtime by profile_selector.py. Each profile is optimised for NVIDIA Cloud NIM Free Tier: temperature calibrated for quality vs creativity balance, max_tokens sized to avoid over-generation, reasoning_budget scaled to task complexity.",

