      "reflection_usage": "on",
      "tool_strategy": "github_for_specific_code",
      "rpm_optimization": "batch_tools_before_nim",
      "why": "Debugging demands the lowest temperature in the system. A debugging response with temperature > 0.3 risks suggesting plausible-sounding but incorrect fixes. High reasoning budget compensates for narrow token diversity by increasing depth of analysis."
